ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: take the class, it's a welcome contrast to anything academic, especially if you are doing a doctorate

FILM 735 is a year long workshop in which you do independent work to develop a documentary project that speaks to your disciplinary interests. I would absolutely recommend it because of the scope of activities that we engage in and the amount of rigorous work we do in this class.
The course provides enough skills to make a documentary film. Anyone interested in documentary filmmaking should consider taking the course.
